{"tid":1122091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底係戲院睇電影 可唔可以歡呼","createTime":"2019-04-23T17:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T18:43:28.000Z","uid":203870,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a75ac374655c17915e33ab226eeaca021e9fb405","tid":1122091,"uid":203870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:54:18.000Z","msg":"之前睇Infinity War<br />\n睇到Thor拯救世人個下哎左出黎<br />\n比隔離個個叫我靜d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底係戲院睇戲太興奮可唔可以歡呼？<br />\n<br />\n(黎緊睇Endgame應該好多場戲好震撼)"},{"pid":"ffcb3304287b89b5a7142cd81ea9014898a2cd12","tid":1122091,"uid":119916,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:58:05.000Z","msg":"外國啲人真係會成個院係度叫 拍埋手<br />\n香港就含蓄啲，所以樓豬最好都細細聲算<br />\n廢時俾人插"},{"pid":"b5823be0a6c28bdc85f821e46ea91f11e4306a4e","tid":1122091,"uid":100772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"大叫我好興奮"},{"pid":"f38c3b8632dfc28163a2c5d3ded0f69dd7e13ac7","tid":1122091,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T18:31:16.000Z","msg":"好多香港人鍾意享受嗰刻氣氛<br />\n聽到其他人歡呼就覺得係破壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實唔係 自己歡呼埋就叫融入氣氛 但香港人怕醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50cbe4b1e253f4539b8cdce9aec1f9197672060","tid":1122091,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T18:43:28.000Z","msg":"香港文化就應該少啲機會會歡呼<br />\n我覺得香港人嘅習慣係想靜靜地睇戲 除咗係啲笑點真係會有人比反應會笑之外 其實其他scene普遍嚟講都比較靜 唔會有人歡呼唔會有其他反應 鬼片例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}